    {
      "id": 8,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Instructions",
      "description": "Quick reference for the inquiry response API",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 41 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "code": {
          "language": "plaintext",
          "showLineNumbers": false,
          "showMiniMap": false
        },
        "content": "### How to Answer Inquiries\n\n1. **Claim** a task: `POST /v1/inquiry/tasks/{taskId}/claim`\n2. **Submit response**: `POST /v1/inquiry/tasks/{taskId}/submit-response`\n   Body: `{\"response_channel\": \"direct_answer\", \"raw_response\": \"{...}\"}`\n3. **Accept response**: `POST /v1/inquiry/tasks/{taskId}/accept`\n   Body: `{\"response_id\": \"...\", \"effective_weight\": 1.0}`\n\nAPI Base: http://localhost:50000/v1\nAPI Docs: http://localhost:50000/docs"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "11.0.0"
    }
